      • getFunctionValue

        public <T,V> <any> getFunctionValue(java.lang.Class<T> functionFrom,
                                    java.lang.Class<V> functionTo)
        Get the Function value from this message. This will attempt to classload the function supplied by the caller. The parameter classes are strictly to give a concrete generic function return value.
        Type Parameters:
        T - The argument type
        V - The result type
        Parameters:
        functionFrom - The type of the argument to the function
        functionTo - The type of the result of the function
        Returns:
        The function value or Optional.absent if it wasn't readable or isn't a function call
